"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-07-olympic-discus-champion-stona-considers-american-football-career\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS,\\u00a0France\\u00a0(AFP) - Jamaican's Olympic discus champion Roje Stona said he was unsure whether to pursue a career in American football despite coming out on top in a thrilling battle at the Paris Games on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.4963279558069429, \"rank\": 0.7062313609970744, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9413765295687107, \"rank\": 0.050107911177211265, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stona threw an Olympic record of 70.00 metres - just three centimetres farther than Lithuania's Mykolas Alekna.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6926416516896582, \"rank\": 0.44292870538944507, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mykolas_Alekna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mykolas Alekna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mykolas_Alekna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mykolas_Alekna\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is what I have been preparing for,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is what I dream of.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To come here and actually do it, it's one of the best feelings of my life.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best day of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 25-year-old said he was undecided on his sporting future.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to sleep on it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stona has had tryouts for hopefuls at NFL teams the Green Bay Packers and the New Orleans Saints.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9996845774839674, \"rank\": 0.00028200439852856153, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Saints\", \"score\": 0.999516990634013, \"rank\": 0.0004299916310349428, \"text\": \"New Orleans Saints\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Saints\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Saints\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was very new to me.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew the Olympic Games were coming up,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have got a lot of thinking to do and do a lot of decisions to make.\\\"\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stona said field events should be more high profile in a sport in which track events often attract most of the attention.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jamaica's Roje Stona competes in the men's discus throw final of the athletics event at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games at Stade de France in Saint-Denis, north of Paris, on August 7, 2024.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9260660309850783, \"rank\": 0.07975491942267803, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999958031859778, \"rank\": 2.2835958686785643e-06, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999652782213, \"rank\": 3.4721883487479046e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo: AFP)  Michael Johnson's lucrative new athletics circuit, being launched in 2025, will only feature track events.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.27532889874352734, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Field events should get more attention, to be honest.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I see something like that, it kind of de-motivates us,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are putting in a lot of work as well, if not more.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not easy.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What we do is very repetitive.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got to do a lot of maintenance.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone has to work hard but we have got to live with the playing field.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you want to keep throwing or do you want to play American football?\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a great question.\\\"\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": []}]}"